data.description: Discover your perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and privacy in this splendid four-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home ideally situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac location. Boasting a coveted setting with no neighbors behind, this residence offers a serene retreat while being conveniently close to shopping centers and a hospital.    Step into this well maintained home and experience the inviting atmosphere created by its well-designed layout. The main level features a spacious living area, a gourmet kitchen equipped with modern appliances, and a dining area perfect for hosting family gatherings or entertaining guests. The master suite is locate on the The main level and its own bathroom.      Upstairs, the three  generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy. The bedrooms are versatile, accommodating various needs such as a home office, workout space, or guest rooms.    Conveniently located near shopping centers, restaurants, and a hospital, this home provides easy access to everyday amenities and essential services. Whether you're seeking a family-friendly neighborhood or a peaceful setting close to urban conveniences, this residence offers the ideal balance     Agent has interest in home.
